[Brocade Odyssey]

2
00:01:27,210 --> 00:01:29,810
[Episode 12]

3
00:01:33,510 --> 00:01:35,510
A rabbit cannot kill a tiger in one bite.

4
00:01:36,630 --> 00:01:38,080
But as long as it isn't found,

5
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,510
it can keep biting.

6
00:01:41,950 --> 00:01:43,190
And there will come a day

7
00:01:43,590 --> 00:01:44,870
when it kills the tiger.

8
00:01:47,550 --> 00:01:48,440
General Niu,

9
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:50,000
the investigation has confirmed

10
00:01:50,190 --> 00:01:51,680
that this is indeed Shu Red Silk.

11
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:56,910
What about the Shu Red plaque at the entrance to the Brocade Bureau?

12
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,040
It should be

13
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:01,310
changed to Mr. Zhao's name.

14
00:02:04,360 --> 00:02:05,190
Very well.

15
00:02:30,060 --> 00:02:37,190
[Zhao Manor]

16
00:02:37,190 --> 00:02:38,030
Yingying!

17
00:02:57,720 --> 00:02:58,800
Did you really dye

18
00:02:59,550 --> 00:03:00,910
the fake Shu Red?

19
00:03:04,550 --> 00:03:05,390
I do, now.

20
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,960
You know what I care about the most.

21
00:03:11,910 --> 00:03:13,190
Yet, you ruined it with your own actions.

22
00:03:17,910 --> 00:03:18,720
Zhao Xiuyuan,

23
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,960
I wish that we hadn't met.

24
00:03:26,670 --> 00:03:27,520
Yingying,

25
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,720
do not go up against those you aren't able to defeat.

26
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:36,110
You will only end up hurting yourself.

27
00:03:36,270 --> 00:03:37,320
Put a stop to this.

28
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:38,910
This is your wedding day.

29
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:40,720
You should say that to your new wife.

30
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:55,390
Of course I know

31
00:03:56,030 --> 00:03:58,600
that the fake Shu Red is a knife pointing towards you.

32
00:04:00,190 --> 00:04:01,440
But if I didn't pick up

33
00:04:02,630 --> 00:04:03,630
this knife,

34
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:05,720
someone else would do it too.

35
00:04:08,730 --> 00:04:13,130
[Color Formula]

36
00:04:29,550 --> 00:04:30,350
Yingying,

37
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,920
stop reading it.

38
00:04:32,110 --> 00:04:33,480
Finish the noodles first.

39
00:04:33,950 --> 00:04:36,230
Leave the rest for tomorrow.

40
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:40,550
Mother,

41
00:04:42,110 --> 00:04:43,600
it was Shu Red Silk.

42
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,550
That was Father's Shu Red Silk.

43
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,510
He is General Niu,

44
00:04:54,070 --> 00:04:55,720
the Vice Commander of a whole state.

45
00:04:56,110 --> 00:04:57,720
He can twist facts and control everyone's fate

46
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,920
just because he is a Vice Commander?

47
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,480
Ji Yingying,

48
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:02,550
how many times have I told you?

49
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:04,160
Don't bring up Shu Red Silk again.

50
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,550
Why can't you keep that in mind?

51
00:05:14,510 --> 00:05:15,390
Finish the noodles

52
00:05:15,510 --> 00:05:16,350
and get some rest.

53
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:30,600
Ting,

54
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,160
keep a close eye on her.

55
00:05:32,390 --> 00:05:33,880
You can't let anything happen to her.

56
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:35,950
Yes, Mum.

57
00:06:36,420 --> 00:06:40,870
[Beloved Husband, Ji Guinan's Memorial Tablet]

58
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:51,320
Guinan,

59
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:54,320
I hope you won't blame me.

60
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,230
I only want our family

61
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:59,320
to have a safe and peaceful life.

62
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:26,110
Father!

63
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:31,790
Father!

64
00:07:42,670 --> 00:07:43,480
Father...

65
00:07:55,950 --> 00:07:56,760
Father!

66
00:07:57,760 --> 00:07:59,000
I am sorry!

67
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:01,670
I could not protect your Shu Red Silk!

68
00:08:13,230 --> 00:08:14,070
Father...

69
00:08:14,070 --> 00:08:15,000
Yingying?

70
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:17,720
Don't be scared,

71
00:08:18,110 --> 00:08:18,920
Yingying.

72
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,350
No!

73
00:09:22,280 --> 00:09:23,080
Father...

74
00:09:25,520 --> 00:09:26,320
I'm sorry...

75
00:09:28,710 --> 00:09:29,550
I'm sorry!

76
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:34,760
Father, I'm sorry...

77
00:09:40,350 --> 00:09:42,150
Father, I'm sorry!

78
00:09:56,110 --> 00:09:57,200
Feel free to come to me

79
00:09:57,670 --> 00:09:58,960
whenever you decide

80
00:10:00,150 --> 00:10:01,080
to look into your father's case.

81
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:18,080
Yaoting,

82
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:19,080
help me.

83
00:10:26,180 --> 00:10:32,550
[Brocade Bureau]

84
00:10:35,210 --> 00:10:38,730
[Flushed Rose, Ji Yingying. Shu Red, Zhao Xiuyuan]

85
00:10:41,620 --> 00:10:48,510
[Brocade Bureau]

86
00:11:05,380 --> 00:11:11,270
[Brocade Bureau]

87
00:11:19,150 --> 00:11:21,550
A rabbit cannot kill a tiger in one bite.

88
00:11:25,590 --> 00:11:27,000
But as long as it isn't found...

89
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,910
It can keep biting.

90
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:31,400
And there will come a day when it kills the tiger.

91
00:11:32,350 --> 00:11:33,520
Future friend?

92
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:38,000
Future friend.

93
00:11:44,590 --> 00:11:45,200
Who threw that at me?

94
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,000
Help me, sir!

95
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,080
He is a kidnapper!

96
00:11:48,110 --> 00:11:49,880
Naughty girl! You are lying again!

97
00:11:50,470 --> 00:11:52,110
He is wearing Hanguang brocade.

98
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:53,550
It is as expensive as gold.

99
00:11:53,910 --> 00:11:55,200
If you call yourself my father,

100
00:11:55,590 --> 00:11:57,110
you should pay him back on my behalf!

101
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:57,960
Pay for it.

102
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:00,790
My child has been acting out.

103
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:03,110
Allow me to apologize on her behalf.

104
00:12:03,550 --> 00:12:05,440
I truly cannot afford to pay for your outfit.

105
00:12:05,710 --> 00:12:07,320
We spent all our money

106
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,470
on her mother's medical bills.

107
00:12:08,470 --> 00:12:10,470
Mister, please forgive us

108
00:12:10,760 --> 00:12:11,710
out of the kindness of your heart.

109
00:12:11,710 --> 00:12:13,110
The poor family's life

110
00:12:13,230 --> 00:12:14,280
is not easy.

111
00:12:14,790 --> 00:12:15,760
Just forgive him!

112
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:16,520
Forgive him!

113
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:18,000
- Forgive him! - Forgive him!

114
00:12:18,400 --> 00:12:19,670
Give her to me as the compensation then.

115
00:12:22,350 --> 00:12:23,080
Hurry up and go home with me!

116
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:23,790
Let me go!

117
00:12:24,110 --> 00:12:24,520
Hey!

118
00:12:25,110 --> 00:12:25,880
Your daughter?

119
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:27,320
Do you know how old she is?

120
00:12:27,550 --> 00:12:28,710
Does she have any scars on her body?

121
00:12:28,710 --> 00:12:30,000
Do you know what she likes to eat or what she cannot eat?

122
00:12:30,470 --> 00:12:31,910
Should we head to the magistrate and clear this up?

123
00:12:32,470 --> 00:12:33,110
Mister,

124
00:12:33,150 --> 00:12:34,550
there's no need for that!

125
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:44,520
Good!

126
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,000
- Good! - Impressive!

127
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:53,640
Mr. Yang,

128
00:12:53,710 --> 00:12:55,110
your father just lost his temper.

129
00:12:55,280 --> 00:12:56,200
That's why he was a little harsh

130
00:12:56,350 --> 00:12:57,320
and punished you more severely!

131
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,520
The messenger only said

132
00:12:59,710 --> 00:13:00,880
that the soldiers surrounded your house!

133
00:13:01,150 --> 00:13:02,470
Perhaps there is a mistake!

134
00:13:08,590 --> 00:13:09,550
You again?

135
00:13:09,670 --> 00:13:10,440
It's you.

136
00:13:10,880 --> 00:13:12,400
Something happened at my home!

137
00:13:12,910 --> 00:13:14,350
Please give me a ride!

138
00:13:25,670 --> 00:13:27,350
If my family survives this crisis,

139
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:30,080
I will definitely befriend you formally.

140
00:13:32,110 --> 00:13:33,320
I will give you a ride

141
00:13:34,080 --> 00:13:35,200
since you are my future friend.

142
00:13:39,350 --> 00:13:40,150
Father!

143
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:44,350
A rabbit cannot kill a tiger in one bite.

144
00:13:45,520 --> 00:13:46,910
But as long as it isn't found,

145
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:49,350
it can keep biting.

146
00:13:50,790 --> 00:13:51,880
And there will come a day

147
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:53,710
when it kills the tiger.

148
00:14:04,910 --> 00:14:06,280
When did you realize it was me?

149
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:08,470
The day after Sang Shisi went riding

150
00:14:08,470 --> 00:14:09,710
by Huanhua Creek.

151
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:11,550
The second time we met.

152
00:14:12,760 --> 00:14:13,880
Why didn't you tell me?

153
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:18,320
Did you already know

154
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,640
they were faking Shu red

155
00:14:20,110 --> 00:14:22,280
and showed it to me at the dyehouse?

156
00:14:24,710 --> 00:14:26,350
Did you also know the Niu family

157
00:14:26,350 --> 00:14:27,960
was involved in my father's death?

158
00:14:30,760 --> 00:14:31,790
You do not tell me anything.

159
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:33,520
You keep everything from me.

160
00:14:33,910 --> 00:14:34,880
You scoundrel!

161
00:14:44,550 --> 00:14:45,440
You have mastered it.

162
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:47,590
This is the first time I use it.

163
00:14:47,590 --> 00:14:48,670
It will not work on me.

164
00:14:58,550 --> 00:14:59,670
What I am doing right now

165
00:15:01,710 --> 00:15:02,590
is really dangerous.

166
00:15:03,150 --> 00:15:03,910
Are you going to stop me

167
00:15:03,910 --> 00:15:05,320
from fighting a battle I cannot possibly win?

168
00:15:08,910 --> 00:15:10,320
All I want you to know is

169
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:11,910
that you are not alone in this.

170
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:13,110
Even if you fall,

171
00:15:13,280 --> 00:15:14,110
you should know

172
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:15,280
where to fall to secure your life.

173
00:15:23,400 --> 00:15:24,670
You knew I would come.

174
00:15:25,710 --> 00:15:26,710
You were waiting for me just now.

175
00:15:26,910 --> 00:15:27,910
Not entirely.

176
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:30,110
What did you discover on the mountain?

177
00:15:31,520 --> 00:15:32,710
Some people keep transporting silk to the mountains.

178
00:15:33,670 --> 00:15:35,280
What do you think they are up to?

179
00:15:35,320 --> 00:15:36,150
The piece of fabric

180
00:15:36,470 --> 00:15:37,760
I showed you that day

181
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:40,280
came from their clothing.

182
00:15:40,280 --> 00:15:42,350
I have sent someone to scout the mountains

183
00:15:42,790 --> 00:15:44,110
to locate the spot you mentioned.

184
00:15:44,150 --> 00:15:45,200
Once we find something...

185
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:46,000
What will you do?

186
00:15:47,470 --> 00:15:48,520
[From Mencius, Section 2, Gongsun Chou, Part Two]
"No matter the opposition,

187
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:51,280
I will go where justice leads."

188
00:15:55,280 --> 00:15:56,030
Yang Jinglan,

189
00:15:58,080 --> 00:15:59,550
promise me one thing.

190
00:15:59,670 --> 00:16:00,790
What do you want me to do?

191
00:16:01,110 --> 00:16:02,080
Let us work together.

192
00:16:02,590 --> 00:16:03,110
Work together?

193
00:16:03,590 --> 00:16:04,520
I can help you look

194
00:16:04,520 --> 00:16:05,520
into whatever you need.

195
00:16:06,280 --> 00:16:07,520
But before we team up,

196
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:09,320
I need to know

197
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:12,150
if your benefactor can protect the Ji family.

198
00:16:18,710 --> 00:16:20,320
How did you know I have a benefactor?

199
00:16:21,910 --> 00:16:23,710
Could I not have done it by myself?

200
00:16:23,710 --> 00:16:25,400
How could you have become a brocade officer on your own?

201
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:31,590
I will use

202
00:16:31,590 --> 00:16:32,840
my own strength

203
00:16:33,030 --> 00:16:34,520
to protect you.

204
00:16:37,470 --> 00:16:39,280
I can take care of myself.

205
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:43,350
I want to dye the true Shu Red Silk.

206
00:16:44,520 --> 00:16:45,520
Will you help me?

207
00:17:02,880 --> 00:17:03,960
After my father's death,

208
00:17:04,070 --> 00:17:05,310
I cannot stand the sight of blood.

209
00:17:05,710 --> 00:17:07,160
The sight of flowing red terrifies me.

210
00:17:07,800 --> 00:17:08,880
That is the reason

211
00:17:08,880 --> 00:17:10,920
why I’ve never succeeded in dyeing Shu Red Silk.

212
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:13,230
Back then,

213
00:17:13,230 --> 00:17:15,040
both of us witnessed my father's death.

214
00:17:16,040 --> 00:17:16,830
Yang Jinglan,

215
00:17:17,710 --> 00:17:19,000
help me overcome this fear.

216
00:17:21,590 --> 00:17:23,190
No matter what happens to me later,

217
00:17:23,190 --> 00:17:24,590
do not stop.

218
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:26,520
Alright!

219
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:57,590
That is mine!

220
00:17:57,830 --> 00:17:59,560
My father left this for me!

221
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:02,070
Ji Yingying!

222
00:18:02,070 --> 00:18:02,880
Stay away!

223
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:08,280
Father,

224
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:09,640
it is your name.

225
00:18:09,640 --> 00:18:10,640
[Shu Red Silk, Ji Guinan]

226
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:12,070
[Flushed Rose, Ji Yingying. Shu Red, Zhao Xiuyuan]
Please, everyone,

227
00:18:12,430 --> 00:18:14,310
take a close look at the red silk in your hands.

228
00:18:14,430 --> 00:18:15,710
This is Shu Red Silk.

229
00:18:15,710 --> 00:18:17,880
It is Shu Red Silk!

230
00:18:18,430 --> 00:18:20,190
Her father created this silk,

231
00:18:20,560 --> 00:18:21,520
which had been lost for years.

232
00:18:22,470 --> 00:18:23,640
Now that someone else has dyed it,

233
00:18:24,070 --> 00:18:25,590
it is only natural for her

234
00:18:26,430 --> 00:18:27,280
to find it hard to accept.

235
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:43,590
Continue!

236
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:04,350
Do not go up against those you cannot defeat.

237
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:06,400
You will only end up hurting yourself.

238
00:19:06,520 --> 00:19:07,640
Put a stop to this.

239
00:19:08,560 --> 00:19:10,680
Ji Guinan is hereby sentenced to immediate execution

240
00:19:10,680 --> 00:19:12,000
for presenting inferior goods as tribute,

241
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:12,950
deceiving the emperor,

242
00:19:13,350 --> 00:19:14,590
and resisting arrest!

243
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:01,190
Father...

244
00:20:02,160 --> 00:20:03,160
I am sorry.

245
00:20:05,760 --> 00:20:08,590
I could not protect your Shu Red Silk.

246
00:20:14,590 --> 00:20:15,400
Father.

247
00:20:21,760 --> 00:20:22,880
Yingying, do not be afraid.

248
00:20:23,820 --> 00:20:25,830
♪Fallen petals, scattered on the ground♪

249
00:20:25,830 --> 00:20:27,470
This is not just the color of blood,

250
00:20:28,190 --> 00:20:29,310
it is also the color

251
00:20:30,280 --> 00:20:32,230
of Shu Red Silk.

252
00:20:32,230 --> 00:20:34,000
♪Like dust in the creek♪

253
00:20:34,170 --> 00:20:37,090
♪it slips away♪

254
00:20:37,090 --> 00:20:37,650
Hold this.

255
00:20:40,420 --> 00:20:42,730
♪Time just spins, tearing at the seams♪

256
00:20:43,210 --> 00:20:44,520
♪I walk through the pain♪

257
00:20:44,520 --> 00:20:47,940
♪but I still chase the dream♪

258
00:20:48,390 --> 00:20:50,940
♪The road is ahead♪

259
00:20:51,090 --> 00:20:55,700
♪but it feels so unknown♪

260
00:20:58,180 --> 00:21:01,610
♪How can we, so small, fight against this tide?♪

261
00:21:01,610 --> 00:21:04,920
♪Holding on tight, as the ropes pull me inside♪

262
00:21:06,710 --> 00:21:13,610
♪To show that the soaring crimson is mine to own♪

263
00:21:14,620 --> 00:21:18,730
♪Red like a vow, that's burning slow♪

264
00:21:18,730 --> 00:21:22,600
♪Silent red, where all my memories go♪

265
00:21:24,760 --> 00:21:25,560
Father!

266
00:21:25,560 --> 00:21:27,260
♪Throw the thread, and let the heartache show♪

267
00:21:27,430 --> 00:21:28,950
I am not afraid!

268
00:21:28,950 --> 00:21:31,250
♪Drowning in this, can't let it go♪

269
00:21:33,950 --> 00:21:35,000
Father...

270
00:21:36,160 --> 00:21:36,920
I am not afraid.

271
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:39,190
♪I walk these miles alone, through sleepless nights♪

272
00:21:39,450 --> 00:21:43,790
♪Love in the wind, alive, it's everywhere we have been♪

273
00:21:43,790 --> 00:21:48,320
♪Red blooms bright, but it dies all alone♪

274
00:21:50,460 --> 00:21:54,580
♪Climbing out of destiny's deepest whirlpool♪

275
00:21:55,680 --> 00:21:56,560
Father, I am not afraid.

276
00:21:56,560 --> 00:21:57,900
♪Break through endless barriers♪

277
00:21:59,700 --> 00:22:07,010
♪Set ablaze that fiery crimson hue♪

278
00:22:07,520 --> 00:22:09,800
I can surely dye Shu Red Silk.

279
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:11,440
♪Red like a vow, that's burning slow♪

280
00:22:11,610 --> 00:22:15,570
♪Silent red, where all my memories go♪

281
00:22:15,570 --> 00:22:20,000
♪Throw the thread, and let the heartache show♪

282
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:24,060
♪Drowning in this, can't let it go♪

283
00:22:24,060 --> 00:22:28,350
